(1, '{\"display\":true,\"header_bg\":null,\"title_color\":null,\"text_color\":null,\"image_place\":\"start\",\"section_title\":{\"en\":\"Improve Your Store. No Coding Necessary.\",\"ger\":\"Verbessern Sie Ihren Shop. Keine Codierung erforderlich.\",\"fr\":\"Am\\u00e9liorez votre magasin. Aucun codage n\\u00e9cessaire.\",\"tr\":\"Ma\\u011fazan\\u0131z\\u0131 Geli\\u015ftirin. Kodlama Gerekmez.\",\"pt\":\"Melhore sua loja. Nenhuma Codifica\\u00e7\\u00e3o Necess\\u00e1ria.\",\"ar\":\"\\u062a\\u062d\\u0633\\u064a\\u0646 \\u0634\\u0631\\u0643\\u062a\\u0643. \\u0644\\u0627 \\u062d\\u0627\\u062c\\u0629 \\u0644\\u0644\\u0628\\u0631\\u0645\\u062c\\u0629 \\u0628\\u0646\\u0641\\u0633\\u0643.\",\"bn\":\"\\u0986\\u09aa\\u09a8\\u09be\\u09b0 \\u09a6\\u09cb\\u0995\\u09be\\u09a8 \\u0989\\u09a8\\u09cd\\u09a8\\u09a4. \\u0995\\u09cb\\u09a8 \\u0995\\u09cb\\u09a1\\u09bf\\u0982 \\u09aa\\u09cd\\u09b0\\u09af\\u09bc\\u09cb\\u099c\\u09a8\\u09c0\\u09af\\u09bc.\",\"ru\":\"\\u0423\\u043b\\u0443\\u0447\\u0448\\u0438\\u0442\\u0435 \\u0441\\u0432\\u043e\\u0439 \\u043c\\u0430\\u0433\\u0430\\u0437\\u0438\\u043d. \\u041a\\u043e\\u0434\\u0438\\u0440\\u043e\\u0432\\u0430\\u043d\\u0438\\u0435 \\u043d\\u0435 \\u0442\\u0440\\u0435\\u0431\\u0443\\u0435\\u0442\\u0441\\u044f.\",\"es\":\"Mejora tu tienda. No es necesaria la codificaci\\u00f3n.\",\"zh\":\"\\u6539\\u5584\\u60a8\\u7684\\u5546\\u5e97\\u3002 \\u65e0\\u9700\\u7f16\\u7801\\u3002\"},\"section_description\":{\"en\":\"Increase checkout conversion rates with dynamic rates at checkout. Show the best selection of couriers, in addition to delivery times and fully landed costs. Learn how checkout drives conversions. Cargo is seamlessly integrated with leading eCommerce platforms and marketplaces. You can manage all your shipments without writing a single line of code. See our integrated platforms.\",\"ger\":\"Erh\\u00f6hen Sie die Konversionsraten an der Kasse mit dynamischen Raten an der Kasse. Zeigen Sie die beste Auswahl an Kurieren, zus\\u00e4tzlich zu Lieferzeiten und vollst\\u00e4ndig angelieferten Kosten. Erfahren Sie, wie der Checkout Conversions f\\u00f6rdert. Cargo ist nahtlos in f\\u00fchrende E-Commerce-Plattformen und Marktpl\\u00e4tze integriert. Sie k\\u00f6nnen alle Ihre Sendungen verwalten, ohne eine einzige Codezeile schreiben zu m\\u00fcssen. Sehen Sie sich unsere integrierten Plattformen an.\",\"fr\":\"Augmentez les taux de conversion de paiement avec des taux dynamiques \\u00e0 la caisse. Affichez la meilleure s\\u00e9lection de coursiers, en plus des d\\u00e9lais de livraison et des co\\u00fbts complets. D\\u00e9couvrez comment le paiement g\\u00e9n\\u00e8re des conversions. Cargo est parfaitement int\\u00e9gr\\u00e9 aux principales plateformes et places de march\\u00e9 de commerce \\u00e9lectronique. Vous pouvez g\\u00e9rer tous vos envois sans \\u00e9crire une seule ligne de code. Voir nos plateformes int\\u00e9gr\\u00e9es.\",\"tr\":\"\\u00d6deme s\\u0131ras\\u0131nda dinamik oranlarla \\u00f6deme d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcm oranlar\\u0131n\\u0131 art\\u0131r\\u0131n. Teslimat s\\u00fcreleri ve tam teslimat maliyetlerine ek olarak en iyi kurye se\\u00e7imini g\\u00f6sterin. \\u00d6deme i\\u015fleminin d\\u00f6n\\u00fc\\u015f\\u00fcmleri nas\\u0131l sa\\u011flad\\u0131\\u011f\\u0131n\\u0131 \\u00f6\\u011frenin. Kargo, \\u00f6nde gelen e-ticaret platformlar\\u0131 ve pazar yerleriyle sorunsuz bir \\u015fekilde entegre edilmi\\u015ftir. Tek sat\\u0131r kod yazmadan t\\u00fcm g\\u00f6nderilerinizi y\\u00f6netebilirsiniz. Entegre platformlar\\u0131m\\u0131za bak\\u0131n.\",\"pt\":\"Aumente as taxas de convers\\u00e3o de checkout com taxas din\\u00e2micas no checkout. Mostre a melhor sele\\u00e7\\u00e3o de correios, al\\u00e9m de prazos de entrega e custos de desembarque completos. Saiba como o checkout gera convers\\u00f5es. O Cargo \\u00e9 perfeitamente integrado \\u00e0s principais plataformas e mercados de com\\u00e9rcio eletr\\u00f4nico. Voc\\u00ea pode gerenciar todas as suas remessas sem es